sub_title: Sitecore developer at Human Digital *Recruitment via Human Digital please*
summary:
Experience:
Application designer and developer for over 10 years.
Languages/environment: C#, ASPX, WCF, ASMX, Workflow (VS2008), SQL (MS SQL server).
Externally consumable services (secure & unsecure).
Maintenance of software written in Visual Foxpro.
Asia & pacific traveler, mostly Indonesia, Malaysia, Australia and Samoa, and therefore used to deal with challenging situations.

Goals:
To be lead developer

Specialties: WCF, Sitecore
application debugging and optimization
